          "Hadith.5374 - Jamil ibn Darraj narrated from Zurara, who said:\nI asked Abu Jafar Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as) about a man who forces himself upon a woman.\nImam (as) said: \"He is to be killed.\""
